<paragraph id="E907AC9AE0E6B1DDD7797D0F19454F50" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Bleichfarbiger Fuchsschwanz</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="8D3E04F961E43D9991F4E1C4DA9898E4" pageId="null" pageNumber="767" type="description">
<paragraph id="68A16106FA4F39F0B21FBF30C4C8B1E0" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="B2B61D83FC74E452B337EF7FCF2FDFA2" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Amaranthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="767" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deflexus">
<emphasis id="C38D7ECCDAC287571CE405406A514774" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">A. deflexus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5) durch folgende Merkmale: 1 
<normalizedToken id="00287972459D3CDE2191A16CB707EF76" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
, oft aufrecht, 
<emphasis id="DEB112F8C3671243F9121F9B37CF6D5B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">kahl.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="E7580E4BCACF901F0128A41549C1A982" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
3; 
<emphasis id="8A0FA9D1AC8CA35194AF8DCF0C179D44" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">
Frucht sich nicht 
<normalizedToken id="BC8A4F4147122935197BCC8D9E563B7E" originalValue="öffnend" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">oeffnend</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="972C379193EFED3CFC2EA1B3C67DC2BC" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer bis Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="92C92FB59BC4BA5F3093E07A21C0907B" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">
<emphasis id="9C6FDCFB432A3F17544CD8A2FBCA2D73" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="EF991A2DAFE5E6D1C0D7B4C3C976B2E3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">34:</emphasis>
Material aus 
<normalizedToken id="8A7448E2BB2C780BB12E3BDE0D83D93F" originalValue="europäischen" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">europaeischen</normalizedToken>
und amerikanischen botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="1B29BC9B02FF3A941EA293DF1EBDF8C7" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Grant 1959a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="784DB786B1C4A5981FA3D911E08504E9" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">
<emphasis id="11EBCB19009D196D62881CD0FFCF136A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="4BC0D0DBCE44F55CD5A9A3F6AFEF50BE" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Amaranthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="767" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="retroflexus">
<emphasis id="5CAD1A0061526DC2AD480BBB33CE5B0F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">A. retroflexus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2271E6B99239E35ABF1B5225B968DDD9" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">
<emphasis id="5420B064266120849A7E9D262E9AF010" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="A10453E71B32CDCCDB9A0206BFB82744" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Amaranthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="767" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="graecizans">
<emphasis id="94CEB3F6FCEBA322F7037CD7A1688A37" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">A. graecizans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6). - Im Gebiet verbreitet und 
<normalizedToken id="8D36FD0E2A9E576F22A6BDDFA0AE8DCB" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A88F4F4C15B6147B0FFE715FB53D0F56" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">
<emphasis id="57DE349120C1415CE2EC2C127B64CF9F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Nach Habitus, Farbe, 
<normalizedToken id="2A6AF382BE8DC9D42FAF35440C374A30" originalValue="Blüten-" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Blueten-</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="7BF3824AD7B5A561D1CAFD7523CCE4B6" originalValue="Fruchtgröße" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Fruchtgroesse</normalizedToken>
werden mehrere 
<normalizedToken id="E9EE96504A2F44D81CE92ECAE6A45A95" originalValue="Varietäten" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">Varietaeten</normalizedToken>
unterschieden. Die im Gebiet vorkommende Sippe wird als 
<taxonomicName id="D77A10268B89B9DE4003EAD4E09BF8F2" authority="(Loisel.) Thell." authorityName="Thell." baseAuthorityName="Loisel." pageId="null" pageNumber="767" rank="variety" variety="ascendens">
var. 
<emphasis id="D2F9CD7613D1DF91B247F76908FAB7D0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="767">ascendens</emphasis>
(Loisel.) Thell.
</taxonomicName>
bezeichnet.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
